You could also make it such that an elf can only fire when within a certain
distance from the forest edge.

As oldschool said, trees tend to stay still and its quite unlikely that
there would be a clear path through a heavy forest in the direction you
wanted to fire *every* time.

Of course you could be creative and make different density forests, mark
that as an interesting point for a game modification :)

